modName: Staff of Magnus - Business as Usual
summary: This mod allows you to trade and do quests with the wizards in the College of Winterhold, even while Ancano is using the Eye of Magnus during the Staff of Magnus quest.
descriptionHtml:
This mod allows you to trade and do quests with the wizards in the College of Winterhold, even while Ancano is using the Eye of Magnus during the Staff of Magnus quest. Never again worry about getting stuck here without the right spells to complete the quest!

(Just to clarify a bit, this does not add any quests.)

It should be compatible with everything.

If there are any issues, leave a comment!
author: Utherix
